metadata.name: Morixels Toy #30
metadata.description:
If you are thinking about having a land and a house in the Morixels Land
You should buy toys for your dogs and cats so that they don't get depressed

If you find the royal crown in this collection, if you bought it in the primary market, any number of toys you bought before buying the crown will be free and the money will be sent to your wallet.

You don't have Morixels?

Don't worry you can buy from the primary or the secondary market üëá

https://www.fxhash.xyz/u/Morteza_Yousefi


The Morixels Toy are unique Random Generated 200 PFP NFTs.
This collection is manually designed.
The original Artwork was designed in 24 by 24 pixels and then resized to 1080 by 1080 resolution.
The number of Traits in this collection is 11 (118 layers) and it has the ability to make 8,494,295,040 NFTs.

Some ‚Äãlayers are less than 1 percent of the total, some 100 percent, and some between 0.1 and 100 percent.

To create balance, these NFTs are randomly minted, and this is a chance for everyone to get a rare version. So due to the low price of these NFTs, if the rare version did not belong to you, it is still possible for you to mint the new NFTs.
To Produce this collection, all the layers were designed pixel by pixel, which was time-consuming and difficult. And this greatly increases the value of this collection.

Because this is an NFT in PFP format, you can put it on your avatar on Twitter or Instagram.

Twitter: @Morixels

Website: https://morixels.com/

Designed by: @morteza_yousefy
Made in 2022

metadata.name: FxPlanet #27
metadata.description:
üü¢„Ä∞Storyline„Ä∞üü¢

Once upon a time, a God had a little daughter. The daughter liked to explore the planets on his father's cosmos. Suddenly the daughter got sick and died like a collapsing star. God gets alone, angry, depressed and finally mad. He turned all the universe to ash and mixed the ash of her daughter's soul with it to make her alive, But he failed. In the end, he decided to destroy himself to make a New cosmos of all generative planets from ash of himself and his daughter's soul to one more time in the eternity they can be with each other in a heart of a planet. If you listen carefully to the planets, you may hear them calling each other.

‚¨õ‚¨õ‚¨õ‚¨õ‚¨õ‚¨õ‚¨õ

üî¥„Ä∞Rarity„Ä∞üî¥

This collection is a 3D generative interactive artwork (Made with Unity Game Engine) that contains of 9999+1 planets (1 shared source of light and 9999 pieces of souls) from billions of variation. You can see more random variations from fxhash page.
‚óº The beauty and complexity of the Planet's surface is important, But what is going on inside?
Each planet has three grades of volume (High, Medium, Low) that show you what resources exist on the planets (Common, Rare, Legendary).
Some resources are so valuable and infrequent.
‚óº For Example: It's possible to get Oxygen (Legendary Resource) on Low volume slot, but it's infrequent if you get it on High volume slot.
